               <p>Q. You acted as his agents, you receive a remuneration for taking care of his concerns - A. I cannot say what my master does.</p>
               <p>Mr. Gurney. Q. Do you know any thing about whether Mr. Mellish paid money into Mr. Moses's hands - A. I know nothing about it, Mr. Moses draws upon his own bankers.</p>
